@function fileTransform
  @added 2.0.0
  @description
    Builds a file transform that takes a @type[File], converts it to HTML and then renames files to make a sensible directory structure for the site.

    For example, a file in @code[directory/file.um] would be converted to HTML as @code[directory/file.html] and then be renamed and output to @code[target/directory/file/index.html]


  @param? options [Object]

  @returns Function
    @param file [File]
